SELECT DISTINCT "c"."account_id" FROM (SELECT "a"."account_id","a"."ip_address" FROM ("loginfo" AS "a") JOIN "loginfo" AS "b" WHERE "a"."account_id"="b"."account_id" AND "a"."ip_address"!="b"."ip_address" AND "a"."login" BETWEEN "b"."login" AND "b"."logout") AS "c"

SELECT DISTINCT "a"."account_id" FROM "loginfo" AS "a" JOIN "loginfo" AS "b" ON "a"."account_id"="b"."account_id" AND ("a"."login" BETWEEN "b"."login" AND "b"."logout" OR "b"."login" BETWEEN "a"."login" AND "a"."logout") WHERE "a"."ip_address"!="b"."ip_address"

SELECT DISTINCT "a"."account_id" FROM ("LogInfo" AS "a") JOIN "LogInfo" AS "b" WHERE "a"."login" BETWEEN ("b"."login") AND ("b"."logout") AND "a"."account_id"="b"."account_id" AND "a"."ip_address"!="b"."ip_address"

WITH "cte_session_overlap" AS (SELECT DISTINCT "l1"."account_id" FROM "LogInfo" AS "l1" JOIN "LogInfo" AS "l2" ON "l1"."account_id"="l2"."account_id" AND "l1"."ip_address"!="l2"."ip_address" AND ("l2"."login" BETWEEN "l1"."login" AND "l1"."logout" OR "l2"."logout" BETWEEN "l1"."login" AND "l1"."logout")) SELECT * FROM "cte_session_overlap"

SELECT "l1"."account_id" FROM "loginfo" AS "l1" JOIN "loginfo" AS "l2" ON "l1"."account_id"="l2"."account_id" AND "l1"."ip_address"!="l2"."ip_address" WHERE "l2"."login" BETWEEN "l1"."login" AND "l1"."logout" GROUP BY "l1"."account_id"

SELECT DISTINCT "a"."account_id" FROM "LogInfo" AS "a" JOIN "LogInfo" AS "b" ON "a"."account_id"="b"."account_id" AND "a"."login"<="b"."login" AND "a"."logout">="b"."login" AND "a"."ip_address"!="b"."ip_address"

WITH "a" AS (SELECT "t1"."account_id","t1"."login" AS "in1","t1"."logout" AS "ou1","t2"."login" AS "in2","t2"."logout" AS "ou2" FROM "loginfo" AS "t1" JOIN "loginfo" AS "t2" ON "t1"."account_id"="t2"."account_id" AND "t1"."ip_address"!="t2"."ip_address") SELECT DISTINCT "account_id" FROM "a" WHERE ("in1" BETWEEN "in2" AND "ou2") OR ("ou1" BETWEEN "in2" AND "ou2")
SELECT DISTINCT "a"."account_id" FROM "LogInfo" AS "a" JOIN "LogInfo" AS "b" USING ("account_id") WHERE "a"."ip_address"!="b"."ip_address" AND ("a"."login" BETWEEN "b"."login" AND "b"."logout")

SELECT DISTINCT "a"."account_id" FROM ("loginfo" AS "a") JOIN "loginfo" AS "b" WHERE "a"."account_id"="b"."account_id" AND "a"."ip_address"!="b"."ip_address" AND "a"."logout">="b"."login" AND "a"."logout"<="b"."logout"

SELECT DISTINCT "a"."account_id" FROM "LogInfo" AS "a" JOIN "LogInfo" AS "b" ON "a"."account_id"="b"."account_id" WHERE "a"."login" BETWEEN "b"."login" AND "b"."logout" AND ("a"."ip_address"!="b"."ip_address")

SELECT DISTINCT "l1"."account_id" FROM "LogInfo" AS "l1" JOIN "LogInfo" AS "l2" ON "l1"."account_id"="l2"."account_id" AND "l1"."ip_address"!="l2"."ip_address" AND "l1"."login"<="l2"."logout" AND "l1"."logout">="l2"."login"
